sequenceDiagram
  actor User as 开发人员
  participant UI as 前端管理台
  participant API as HTTP API
  participant Store as store.json
  participant Summary as SummaryService

  User->>UI: 提交调用登记表单
  UI->>API: POST /api/calls
  API->>Store: readStore()
  API->>API: 校验 providerId 和 modelId
  API->>Store: writeStore(call)
  API->>Summary: computeSummary(store)
  Summary->>Summary: enrichCall() 计算费用和缓存节省
  Summary-->>API: summary
  API-->>UI: state + summary
  UI-->>User: 刷新总览、报表和调用列表
